extendedInfo.description: The Dallas IIA Chapter has a long history of providing the highest quality programs at a very reasonable price. The 1st annual Dallas IIA Super Conference will be the biggest and most ambitious CPE event in our history. It will be a forum where you and other top leaders of our profession can discuss emerging risks and solutions to the latest challenges impacting the profession. This event will create an annual tradition for the chapter that will not only provide an educational experience that is beyond your expectations, but also a networking event that will include many major sponsors leading the internal audit profession. Plans are also to have the IIA Research Foundation bookstore onsite allowing you to review and purchase any of the latest IIA publications at a discounted price.Keywords: IIA Dallas, Super Conference, internal auditors, Dallas, Texas, 2012
